data.description:
Discover the charm of this delightful townhome in a vibrant neighborhood with an array of amenities. Enjoy the convenience of being just moments away from shopping, restaurants, and recreational spots, while also being in close proximity to Downtown Matthews and easy access to Hwy 485.
This well maintained home boasts numerous upgrades, including a renovated primary bathroom shower, a replaced HVAC system under warranty until 2026, ensuring peace of mind for the new homeowner.
Other updates include new outdoor lights (2023), water heater replacement in 2021, and refrigerator, and dishwasher all replaced in 2020. New primary bedroom windows in 2020, along with new carpet, kitchen counters, cabinets, and sink in 2016. Fresh interior paint and replacement windows in all other rooms were completed in 2022. 
Take the opportunity to make this well-appointed residence your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and style this property has to offer.
